chunks.title: Section 1 - Short title
chunks.structure_path: Income Tax (Deferred Interest Securities) (Tax File Number Withholding Tax) Act 1991 > Section 1
chunks.text: This Act may be cited as the Income Tax (Deferred Interest Securities) (Tax File Number Withholding Tax) Act 1991.

chunks.title: Section 2 - Commencement
chunks.structure_path: Income Tax (Deferred Interest Securities) (Tax File Number Withholding Tax) Act 1991 > Section 2
chunks.text: This Act commences, or is taken to have commenced, as the case requires, on the commencement of section  221YHZR of the Income Tax Assessment Act 1936.

chunks.title: Section 3 - Act to bind Crown
chunks.structure_path: Income Tax (Deferred Interest Securities) (Tax File Number Withholding Tax) Act 1991 > Section 3
chunks.text: This Act binds the Crown in the right of each of the States, of the Australian Capital Territory and of the Northern Territory.

chunks.title: Section 4 - Imposition of tax
chunks.structure_path: Income Tax (Deferred Interest Securities) (Tax File Number Withholding Tax) Act 1991 > Section 4
chunks.text: Tax payable in accordance with section  14-55 in Schedule 1 to the Taxation Administration Act 1953 is imposed.
